#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.12:3.1"
msgid "Tayo kho me, gāmaṇi, kāmabhogino santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "There are these three kinds of pleasure seekers in the world."

msgctxt "sn42.12:3.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn42.12:3.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, gāmaṇi, ekacco kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati, sāhasena "
"adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena na attānaṃ sukheti na pīṇeti na "
"saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti."
msgstr ""
"Take a pleasure seeker who seeks wealth using illegitimate, coercive means, "
"and who doesn’t make themselves happy and pleased, or share it and make "
"merit."

msgctxt "sn42.12:3.4"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, gāmaṇi, ekacco kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena."
msgstr ""
"Next, a pleasure seeker seeks wealth using illegitimate, coercive means."

msgctxt "sn42.12:3.5"
msgid ""
