msgid ""
"Sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā paccattaṃ veditabbā "
"viññūhi."
msgstr ""
"This wearing away is realizable in this very life, immediately effective, "
"inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know it for "
"themselves."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.6"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ duṭṭho dosādhikaraṇaṃ attabyābādhāyapi ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti."
msgstr ""
"A hateful person, because of hate, intends to hurt themselves, hurt others, "
"and hurt both."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.7"
msgid ""
"Dose pahīne nevattabyābādhāya ceteti, na parabyābādhāya ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāya ceteti."
msgstr "When they’ve given up hate they don’t have such intentions."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.8"
msgid ""
"Sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā paccattaṃ veditabbā "
"viññūhi."
msgstr ""
"This wearing away is realizable in this very life, immediately effective, "
"inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know it for "
"themselves."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.9"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ mūḷho mohādhikaraṇaṃ attabyābādhāyapi ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti."
msgstr ""
"A deluded person, because of delusion, intends to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.10"
msgid ""
"Mohe pahīne nevattabyābādhāya ceteti, na parabyābādhāya ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāya ceteti."
msgstr "When they’ve given up delusion they don’t have such intentions."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.11"
msgid ""
"Sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā paccattaṃ veditabbā "
"viññūhi."
msgstr ""
"This wearing away is realizable in this very life, immediately effective, "
"inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know it for "
"themselves."

msgctxt "sn42.12:22.12"
msgid ""
"Imā kho, gāmaṇi, tisso sandiṭṭhikā nijjarā akālikā ehipassikā opaneyyikā "
"paccattaṃ veditabbā viññūhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the three kinds of wearing away that are realizable in this very "
"life, immediately effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible "
"people can know them for themselves.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.12:23.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rāsiyo gāmaṇi bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Rāsiya the chief said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn42.12:23.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn42.12:23.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn42.12:23.4"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
